author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Is Star Wars Starfighter just a backdoor Rey movie? The latest rumours definitely suggest so. Meanwhile, Emma Watson just got completely destroyed by none other than JK Rowling, and Netflix mass cancellations are biting hard as the backlash against controversial programming grows. Join me, MauLer, Disparu, Chris Gore and Stuttering Craig for Open Bar episode 159.

title: Open Bar #159 - Rey's Starfighter, Emma Watson Blasted, Netflix Collapse?
